        "title": "Bundesliga 2025-26",
        "shortDescription": "Hamburger SV hosts Bayer Leverkusen in the rescheduled Bundesliga Matchday 17 fixture, originally postponed in January due to extreme thawing causing safety risks. Both teams enter seeking a response after recent winless outings, with HSV aiming to ease relegation pressures and Leverkusen chasing Champions League spots. Find out who comes on top. Tune it to catch all the action from Bundesliga 2025-26, LIVE on Sony LIV.",
